&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;&lt;!-- DIV {margin:0px;} --&gt;&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-family:times new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;P&gt;Cyclonus continued to hang in midair, his long ranged scanners and his communications with the sweeps giving him up to the nano-second reports of the conflict at the Black Fortress. He was pleased, all was going according to plan. &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;With a thought he activated his communications gear, &quot;Scourge. Report, have you locted Rodimus?&quot;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&quot;Hmph.&quot; came the sweep commander&#39;s replied. &quot;The coward must have had stealth gear. I cannot detect him directly. But I am picking up his trail heading away from this area. He must be on the run!&quot;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Cyclonus&#39;s voice is calm as he responded, &quot;Do not assume he is running from you, there may be some other purpose. Proceed with caution.&quot;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Scourge grunted, &quot;We will get him. Scourge out!&quot; &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Cyclonus could hear Scourge&#39;s confidant chuckle as the channel closed, leaving Cyclonus to smile inwardly at the confidance of Scourge. &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&quot;Sir.&quot; Tumult&#39;s voice crackled over Cyclonus&#39; internal speakers, &quot;We have failed to achieve our objective. The ark was&nbsp;defended by some someone called Legacy. We would have took him out but the Maximals showed up as well, out flanking us.&quot;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Cyclonus paused, as a part of his plan was not going as he had engieneered. &quot;What is the status of your team, and why isn&#39;t Deepstryke reporting?&quot; Cyclonus called back on the same channel.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&quot;He is critcally damaged sir, the rest of us have recieved minor damage as well. Phobia is looking after him.&quot;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Cyclonus listened intently to the report, tactically asssing how he could best use this. &quot;Where are the other two minions, Darkfate and Nightstrike?&quot;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Tumult grunted, &quot;I gave the command to retreat, but those two defied me and stayed behind. they are probrably being blown to atoms by now!&quot;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&quot;Have Phobia take Deepstryke back to the Moonbase, he will be of little further use to us here. The rest of you rejoin me here.&quot;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&quot;Sir!&quot; came Tumult&#39;s quick reply. &quot;We are on our way.&quot;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Opening up another channel Cyclonus spoke, &quot;Change of plans, move to intercept Darkfate and Nightstike. Acertain thier condition. Aid them as required.&quot; &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&quot;Acknowledged. Enroute.&quot; Came the quick reply and the channel closed.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Nightstrike and Darkfate&nbsp;would be punished later, Cyclonus thought to himself, but for now they would need to be rescued from thier foolishness, and&nbsp;Nightrazor should be sufficiently repaired for this mission.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Cyclonus continued to chuckle as he floated in midair, his sweeps surrounding him like a blanket of energized death, yes things were still according to plan. He would destroy this Rodimus once and for all, and then all the defenders that held them back from the ultimate conquest of earth!&lt;/P&gt;
